name: Nishi
description:
AYAHUASCA TRIP.
In the bowels of the jungle live a large number of sacred spirits, many of them possessing magical powers, which are worthy of respect and devotion by the indigenous people. Some of them are so important that it would be disrespectful just to say their name.
Fifth token of this collection "ENTEOGENOS THROUGH TIMES" dedicated to the Shipibo community of the peruvian Amazon. Thanks for sharing medicine with the world.
